title: National Programs for Science and Technology
summary: The article describes various national programs in China for science and technology research and development, including the Key Technologies Research and Development Program, the 863 Program, the 973 Program, the Torch Program, and the Spark Program.
likely_naics_codes: Likely NAICS Codes: 541710 - Research and Development in the Physical, Engineering, and Life Sciences, 611310 - Colleges, Universities, and Professional Schools, 813910 - Business Associations, 928110 - National Security
